<p id="Synthetic_Biology"> </p>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<p class="header_box">Synthetic Biology</p>
<p>Re-engineered riboswitches that no longer respond to cellular metabolites, but that instead can be controlled by synthetic molecules, are potentially useful gene regulatory tools for use in synthetic biology and biotechnology fields.<br /></p>

